                    ></path>
                </g></svg
            >

            <p class="text-center leading-tight text-[14px]">
                Sobrecalentamiento de CRM en tanque de reacción
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between h-[136px]">
            <svg
                fill="#c91c1c"
                width="128"
                height="128"
                viewBox="0 0 32 32"
                version="1.1"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                ><g id="SVGRepo_bgCarrier" stroke-width="0"></g><g
                    id="SVGRepo_tracerCarrier"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"></g><g id="SVGRepo_iconCarrier">
                    <title>number12</title>
                    <path
                        d="M16 3c-7.18 0-13 5.82-13 13s5.82 13 13 13 13-5.82 13-13-5.82-13-13-13zM18.995 21.357c-0.826 0.797-1.854 1.194-3.086 1.194-1.166 0-2.133-0.335-2.9-1.005-0.769-0.67-1.214-1.545-1.337-2.627l2.391-0.289c0.076 0.607 0.281 1.071 0.616 1.393 0.333 0.321 0.738 0.482 1.213 0.482 0.51 0 0.939-0.194 1.289-0.582 0.348-0.387 0.522-0.909 0.522-1.566 0-0.621-0.167-1.115-0.501-1.479-0.335-0.364-0.742-0.545-1.223-0.545-0.317 0-0.695 0.062-1.136 0.184l0.272-1.997c0.668 0.018 1.178-0.127 1.529-0.434s0.526-0.715 0.526-1.224c0-0.433-0.128-0.777-0.385-1.035-0.258-0.257-0.599-0.386-1.025-0.386-0.421 0-0.779 0.146-1.077 0.438s-0.479 0.72-0.544 1.281l-2.281-0.386c0.158-0.782 0.397-1.407 0.717-1.875s0.765-0.835 1.336-1.103 1.212-0.401 1.921-0.401c1.213 0 2.186 0.387 2.918 1.161 0.604 0.633 0.905 1.348 0.905 2.145 0 1.131-0.619 2.034-1.858 2.708 0.739 0.158 1.33 0.513 1.772 1.063 0.443 0.551 0.664 1.215 0.664 1.994 0.001 1.132-0.412 2.095-1.238 2.891z"
                    ></path>
                </g></svg
            >
            <p class="text-center leading-tight">
                Entrada y calentamiento <br />
                del asfalto
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between h-[136px]">
            <svg
                fill="#ca1c1c"
                width="128"
                height="128"
                viewBox="0 0 32 32"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
                <path
                    d="M16 3c-7.18 0-13 5.82-13 13s5.82 13 13 13 13-5.82 13-13-5.82-13-13-13zM15.9 22.5v-2.6h-5.4v-2.2l5.7-8.3h2.1v8.3h1.6v2.2h-1.6v2.6h-2.4zM15.9 17.7v-4.5l-3 4.5h3z"
                ></path>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-center leading-tight">
                Mezclado de <br />
                alto corte
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between h-[136px]">
            <svg
                fill="#ca1c1c"
                width="128"
                height="128"
                viewBox="0 0 32 32"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
                <path
                    d="M16 3c-7.18 0-13 5.82-13 13s5.82 13 13 13 13-5.82 13-13-5.82-13-13-13zM11.8 19.4l2.4-0.2c0.1 0.7 0.4 1.2 0.8 1.6 0.4 0.4 0.9 0.5 1.4 0.5 0.6 0 1.1-0.2 1.5-0.7 0.4-0.5 0.6-1.2 0.6-2.1 0-0.8-0.2-1.5-0.6-1.9-0.4-0.4-0.9-0.7-1.6-0.7-0.8 0-1.5 0.4-2.2 1.1l-1.9-0.3 1.2-6.5h6.2v2.2h-4.4l-0.4 2.1c0.6-0.3 1.2-0.5 1.8-0.5 1.2 0 2.2 0.4 3 1.3 0.8 0.9 1.2 2 1.2 3.4 0 1.2-0.3 2.2-1 3.1-0.9 1.2-2.2 1.8-3.8 1.8-1.3 0-2.4-0.4-3.2-1.1-0.8-0.7-1.3-1.7-1.5-3z"
                ></path>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-center leading-tight">
                Incorporación a <br />
                tambor mezclador
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between h-[136px]">
            <svg
                fill="#ca1c1c"
                width="128"
                height="128"
                viewBox="0 0 32 32"
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            >
                <path
                    d="M16 3c-7.18 0-13 5.82-13 13s5.82 13 13 13 13-5.82 13-13-5.82-13-13-13zM20.3 12.7l-2.3 0.3c-0.1-0.5-0.3-0.9-0.6-1.2-0.3-0.3-0.7-0.4-1.1-0.4-0.6 0-1.1 0.3-1.5 0.8-0.4 0.5-0.6 1.7-0.7 3.3 0.6-0.7 1.4-1 2.4-1 1.1 0 2 0.4 2.8 1.2 0.8 0.8 1.2 1.9 1.2 3.2 0 1.4-0.4 2.5-1.2 3.4-0.8 0.9-1.9 1.3-3.2 1.3-1.4 0-2.6-0.5-3.5-1.6-0.9-1.1-1.4-2.9-1.4-5.4 0-2.6 0.5-4.5 1.5-5.7 1-1.2 2.2-1.8 3.8-1.8 1.1 0 2 0.3 2.7 0.9 0.7 0.6 1.2 1.5 1.4 2.7zM14.4 18.4c0 0.8 0.2 1.5 0.6 2 0.4 0.5 0.9 0.7 1.4 0.7 0.5 0 0.9-0.2 1.3-0.6 0.3-0.4 0.5-1 0.5-1.9 0-0.9-0.2-1.6-0.5-2-0.4-0.4-0.8-0.6-1.3-0.6-0.5 0-0.9 0.2-1.3 0.6-0.5 0.4-0.7 1-0.7 1.8z"
                ></path>
            </svg>
            <p class="text-center leading-tight">
                Colocación <br /> en carretera
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-b from-[#f4f5f6] to-[#383838] w-full h-[200px]">
    </div>

    <div
        class="bg-[#383838] w-full text-center flex flex-col pt-5 gap-2 md:gap-4"
    >
        <h2 class="text-[#fffaea] font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl">
            Sea el único en el mercado en ofrecer una mezcla que no se puede
            igualar
        </h2>
        <h2 class="text-white font-normal text-lg">
            Con Triaso, conviértase en el proveedor preferido de mezcla
            asfáltica para todos los proyectos de pavimentación en su región.
        </h2>
    </div>
    <div
        class="bg-[#383838] w-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-8 py-10"
    >
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 overflow-hidden relative">
            <!-- BOTÓN IZQUIERDA -->
            <button
                id="prevBtn"
                class="absolute left-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-10 bg-black/70 text-white w-10 h-10 rounded-full"
            >
                ←
            </button>

            <!-- BOTÓN DERECHA -->
            <button
                id="nextBtn"
                class="absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-10 bg-black/70 text-white w-10 h-10 rounded-full"
            >
                →
            </button>

            <div
                class="flex gap-4 transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out"
                id="sliderTrack"
            >
                <!-- Card 1-A -->
                <div
                    class="card w-full sm:w-[calc((100%-32px)/3)] flex-shrink-0 relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden"
                    data-card="0-0"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full h-80 bg-black/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400" alt="" class="object-fill" />
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-3"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="font-bold text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-wide leading-tight mb-2"
                        >
                            Tolva de hule
                        </span>
                        <button
                            class="mostrar-mas flex items-center gap-1 text-white/80 text-xs hover:text-white transition-colors"
                            aria-expanded="false"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="chevron w-3 h-3 transition-transform duration-300"
                                viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                                fill="none"
                            >
                                <path
                                    d="M2 4l4 4 4-4"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    stroke-width="1.8"
                                    stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                            </svg>
                            mostrar más
                        </button>
                        <div
                            class="expandible max-h-0 overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out"
                        >
                            <p
                                class="text-white/75 text-xs leading-relaxed mt-2"
                            >
                                Recibe y almacena el caucho molido (CRM) antes
                                de su dosificación. Incluye rejilla separadora
                                de sobretamaños para garantizar la granulometría
                                adecuada.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 2-B -->
                <div
                    class="card w-full sm:w-[calc((100%-32px)/3)] flex-shrink-0 relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden"
                    data-card="0-1"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full h-80 bg-black/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400" alt="" />
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-3"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="font-bold text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-wide leading-tight mb-2"
                        >
                            Gusano dosificador
                        </span>
                        <button
                            class="mostrar-mas flex items-center gap-1 text-white/80 text-xs hover:text-white transition-colors"
                            aria-expanded="false"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="chevron w-3 h-3 transition-transform duration-300"
                                viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                                fill="none"
                            >
                                <path
                                    d="M2 4l4 4 4-4"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    stroke-width="1.8"
                                    stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                            </svg>
                            mostrar más
                        </button>
                        <div
                            class="expandible max-h-0 overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out"
                        >
                            <p
                                class="text-white/75 text-xs leading-relaxed mt-2"
                            >
                                Transporta el CRM desde la tolva al mezclador de
                                forma controlada y sincronizada con la bomba de
                                asfalto, ambos de velocidad variable.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 3-C -->
                <div
                    class="card w-full sm:w-[calc((100%-32px)/3)] flex-shrink-0 relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden"
                    data-card="0-2"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full h-80 bg-black/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400" alt="" />
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-3"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="font-bold text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-wide leading-tight mb-2"
                        >
                            Calentador de asfalto
                        </span>
                        <button
                            class="mostrar-mas flex items-center gap-1 text-white/80 text-xs hover:text-white transition-colors"
                            aria-expanded="false"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="chevron w-3 h-3 transition-transform duration-300"
                                viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                                fill="none"
                            >
                                <path
                                    d="M2 4l4 4 4-4"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    stroke-width="1.8"
                                    stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                            </svg>
                            mostrar más
                        </button>
                        <div
                            class="expandible max-h-0 overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out"
                        >
                            <p
                                class="text-white/75 text-xs leading-relaxed mt-2"
                            >
                                Eleva el asfalto liquido a su temperatura óptima
                                de incorporación antes de entrar al mezclador.
                                Control preciso de temperatura programable.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 4-D -->
                <div
                    class="card w-full sm:w-[calc((100%-32px)/3)] flex-shrink-0 relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden"
                    data-card="0-3"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full h-80 bg-black/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400" alt="" />
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-3"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="font-bold text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-wide leading-tight mb-2"
                        >
                            Mezclador molecular
                        </span>
                        <button
                            class="mostrar-mas flex items-center gap-1 text-white/80 text-xs hover:text-white transition-colors"
                            aria-expanded="false"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="chevron w-3 h-3 transition-transform duration-300"
                                viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                                fill="none"
                            >
                                <path
                                    d="M2 4l4 4 4-4"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    stroke-width="1.8"
                                    stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                            </svg>
                            mostrar más
                        </button>
                        <div
                            class="expandible max-h-0 overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out"
                        >
                            <p
                                class="text-white/75 text-xs leading-relaxed mt-2"
                            >
                                Corazón del equipo. Integra molecularmente el
                                CRM con el asfalto mediante fuerzas de corte
                                intenso para producir una mezcla homogénea y
                                estable.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 5-E -->
                <div
                    class="card w-full sm:w-[calc((100%-32px)/3)] flex-shrink-0 relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden"
                    data-card="0-4"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full h-80 bg-black/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400" alt="" />
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-3"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="font-bold text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-wide leading-tight mb-2"
                        >
                            Bomba de asfalto 2"
                        </span>
                        <button
                            class="mostrar-mas flex items-center gap-1 text-white/80 text-xs hover:text-white transition-colors"
                            aria-expanded="false"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="chevron w-3 h-3 transition-transform duration-300"
                                viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                                fill="none"
                            >
                                <path
                                    d="M2 4l4 4 4-4"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    stroke-width="1.8"
                                    stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                            </svg>
                            mostrar más
                        </button>
                        <div
                            class="expandible max-h-0 overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out"
                        >
                            <p
                                class="text-white/75 text-xs leading-relaxed mt-2"
                            >
                                Bomba de engranes de 2" que impulsa el cemento
                                asfáltico desde el tanque de entrada al
                                mezclador con flujo variable y controlado.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 6-F -->
                <div
                    class="card w-full sm:w-[calc((100%-32px)/3)] flex-shrink-0 relative rounded-lg overflow-hidden"
                    data-card="0-5"
                >
                    <div
                        class="w-full h-80 bg-black/10 flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400" alt="" />
                    </div>
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/80 via-black/20 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-end p-3"
                    >
                        <span
                            class="font-bold text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-wide leading-tight mb-2"
                        >
                            Gusano removedor 15 Hp
                        </span>
                        <button
                            class="mostrar-mas flex items-center gap-1 text-white/80 text-xs hover:text-white transition-colors"
                            aria-expanded="false"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="chevron w-3 h-3 transition-transform duration-300"
                                viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                                fill="none"
                            >
                                <path
                                    d="M2 4l4 4 4-4"
                                    stroke="currentColor"
                                    stroke-width="1.8"
                                    stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                            </svg>
                            mostrar más
                        </button>
                        <div
                            class="expandible max-h-0 overflow-hidden transition-[max-height] duration-300 ease-out"
                        >
                            <p
                                class="text-white/75 text-xs leading-relaxed mt-2"
                            >
                                Motor de 5-15 Hp que mantiene el asfalto ahulado
                                en movimiento dentro del tanque de
                                almacenamiento, evitando asentamientos del CRM.
                            </p>
                        </div>
